<html><head><title>The Economist: cover credit</title><img src="http://www.economist.com/econlogosmall.gif" alt="The Economist Logo"></td><td align=right valign=top></head><body bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><ol><br><h2><i>The Economist</i>&#160;: cover credit</h2><p>March 2nd - 8th 1996<p><img src="cov02-03-96.jpg" alt="The Economist cover image"><p>The image on this week's cover is:</p><p>Terrorism: &#160; James Walker/For <i>The Economist</i></p><p>All Rights Reserved</p><p><a href="http://www.economist.com/index.html"><i>The Economist</i> Home Page</a> &nbsp; - &nbsp; <a href="http://www.economist.com/cgi-bin/search_form.cgi?825717600,iss">Search</a></p></ol></td></body></html>
