<html><head><title>Contents Page</title></head><body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">

<h2 align=center>
<table width=100% cellpadding=15><tr><td valign=top align=center><img src="cov06-07-96.jpg" width=120 height=159 alt="Issue Cover"><br>
<font size=1><a href="covcredit.html">credit</a></font></td><td valign=top><a href="ld1.html"><b>On the cover</b></a><br>
