<html>
<head>
<title> The Network
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="FFFFFF" text="000000" link="2A4572" alink="2A4572" vlink="587CA3">
<table cellpadding=6>                                                           
<tr>                                                                            
<td>                                                                            
<img align=middle src="/images/logo3.gif">                                 
<td>                                                                            
<img align=middle src="/images/osi_network.gif" alt="The Network">   
</td>                                                                           
</tr>                                                                           
</table>                                                                        
<blockquote>
The more than 24 independent foundations and other nonprofit organizations 
created and funded by philanthropist 
<a href="gsbio.html"><b>George Soros</b></a> are linked together in an 
informal network. At the heart of this network are 24 autonomous foundations 
located in 
<a href="found.html"><b>
Albania, Belarus, Bulgaria, Bosnia & Herzegovina, Croatia, the Czech Republic, 
Estonia, Georgia, Haiti, Hungary, Kazakstan, Kyrgyzstan, Latvia, Lithuania, 
Macedonia, Moldova, Poland, Romania, Russia, Slovakia, Slovenia, South Africa, 
Ukraine, and Yugoslavia
</b></a>.
These foundations all share the common mission of supporting the development of 
<a href="open_society.html"><b>open society</b></a>.
To this end, they operate and support an array of programs in education, 
media, health care, Internet and e-mail communication, human rights, 
arts and culture, and economic and legal reform. 
</blockquote>
