<td>
<a href="gopher://gopher.soros.org/0/General_Info/Publications/OSNews/OSNews_Sum_96.txt"><h3>Open Society News - Summer 1996</h3></a>
<b>
<ul> 
<li>OSI's New U.S. Initiatives
<li>The Open Society Archives
<li>Net Pals
<li>The Schweitzer Institute
<li>Photo Essay - 
<a href="http://pathfinder.com/@@klMKTgcArA3aZ**c/twep/artslink/exhibitions/
