<head>
   <title>University Internet Centers (Russia)
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="FFFFFF" link="2A4572" alink="2A4572" vlink="587CA3">
<table cellpadding=6>                                              
<tr>                                                               
<td>                                                               
<img valign=middle src=/images/logo3.gif alt=#>                    
<td>                                                               
<img valign=middle src=/images/uic.gif alt="University Internet Centers in Russia">
</td>                                                              
</tr>                                                              
