</DOCHDR>
<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN">
<html>
<head>
<title>
LEGPHIL-Philosophy of Law Mailing List
</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="FFFFFF" text="000000" link="2F7348" alink="2F7348" vlink="5D8B6B">
<table cellpadding=6>                                              
<tr>                                                               
<td>                                                               
<img align=middle src="/images/logo3.gif">                    
<td>                                                               
<h1>LEGPHIL-Philosophy of Law Mailing List</h1>
</td>                                                              
</tr>                                                              
</table>                                                           
LEGPHIL is a new academic mailing list on all topics related to philosophy
of law. It is for both discussion and bibliographical reference in the
field of legal philosophy, legal theory, methods of law, sociology of law,
etc.<p>
To subscribe send email to:<br>
<address><a href="mailto:majordomo@lists.lrz-muenchen.de"><b>majordomo@lists.lrz-muenchen.de</b></a></address>                                   
In the body of the message type:<br>
        subscribe legphil FIRSTNAME LASTNAME<br>
