<title>
The East-West Management Institute 
and the Soros Business and Management Foundation
</title> 
</head>
<body bgcolor="FFFFFF" text="000000" link="2A4572" alink="2A4572" vlink="587CA3">
<table cellpadding=6>                                                
<tr>                                                                 
<td>                                                                 
<img align=middle src="/images/logo3.gif">                      
