<a href="gopher://gopher.soros.org/11/Affiliated_Orgs/Other_Affil_Org/Economic_Trans"><img align=middle src="/images/gopher.gif"> Soros Training for Economic Transformation Network</a>
</h3>
<address>Henrik Sterniczuk, Executive Director</address>
<br>
Vul. Eugene Pottier 20<br>
252057 Kyiv<br>
