<blockquote>                                                                    
<i>
The Forced Migration Monitor concentrates on migration issues primarily in the 
Newly Independent States and the Baltics, but in other areas of the world as 
well.
</i>
<p>
Current and back issues of the <A href="migrate.html"><b>Forced Migration Projects'</b>
</a> <cite>Forced Migration Monitor</cite> can be found on this page, along 
with the tables of contents. To find out more about the <cite>Forced Migration Monitor</cite>,
send e-mail to <a href="mailto:refugee@sorosny.org">refugee@sorosny.org</a>.
<p>   
Click <a href="Architext/AT-Open_Society_Institute_Web_Spacequery.html"><b>here</b></a> to search the OSI Web Site.
</blockquote>                                                                   
