<a href="http://www.ilasll.umn.edu/bashiri/iraj.html"><b> Home Page of Iraj Bashiri</b></a><b> Professor at University of Minnesota Institute of Linguistics and Asian and Slavic Languages</b><img align=top src="new1.gif">
</blockquote>  

