<DOCHDR>
http://server.soros.org:80/personal.html 204.168.83.130 19970112101016 text/html 15221
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 12 Jan 1997 10:04:07 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
